# Ollama Local AI SaaS Setup

## Requisitos
- Docker
- Docker Compose

## 1. Clonar o copiar este proyecto
```bash
cd ollama_saas_project
```

## 2. Levantar todo
```bash
docker compose up -d --build
```

## 3. Verificar servicios
```bash
docker ps
```

## 4. Probar API
```bash
curl http://localhost:8081/health
```

## 5. Acceder UI
http://localhost:3000

## 6. Probar Ollama
```bash
curl http://localhost:11434/api/tags
```

## 7. Detener
```bash
docker compose down
```
